             Peer Review 
            Greg P. Smestad, Ph.D. is the lead author of a Solar Energy Materials 
            and Solar Cells (Elsevier) editorial that summarizes key research 
            issues, and requirements for priority publishing in this peer-reviewed 
            journal. 
             
             
            
            
               
             
            Solar Energy Materials and Solar Cells 
            An International Journal devoted to the promotion of photovoltaic 
            (PV), photothermal and photochemical solar energy conversion 
             
             
            
            
              
                 
               
